config DRM_P4
	tristate "Private Eye P4 Display via SPI Interface"
	depends on DRM && SPI
	select DRM_GEM_DMA_HELPER
	select DRM_KMS_HELPER
	help
	  DRM driver for the P4 rotated monochrome head-mounted display
	  connected via SPI. The display is 720x280 but mounted rotated
	  90 degrees, so appears as 280x720 to the hardware.

	  To compile this as a module, choose M here. The module will
	  be called drm_p4.

	  If unsure, say N.
